on history. We cannot rule out a low\nrate in the past SF but we can safely conclude that the last 1-2 Gyr have been\npeculiar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2005 20:00:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
