 amplitudes of the variations are small. If the small\nvariations in Y, Zr, and Ba are indeed real, then the synthesis of the Al\nanomalies must have taken place within an unknown class of stars that also ran\nthe s-process. [Abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2005 14:09:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
